      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the professionals. they don't get it. they think there's a way back up and a way to rebuild, but there isn't. i'm staring at the wreckage and it's just... it's too much. like, i'm already at the absolute bottom. there's nothing left to do but just stay here in the dark.",
