      "content": "it just feels like everyone is just offering me temporary bandages for a wound that's too deep. they keep talking about \"moving forward\" or \"rebuilding\" but that's just more work. more struggle. i'm just so tired of fighting. i feel like i've finally reached the end of the line and there's nowhere else to go.",
